Description: Canvas based on Clutter and Gtk+ 3.0
URL: https://github.com/Philip-Scott/libgtkcanvas
Version: @VERSION@
Requires: gtk+3.0 >= 3.22.11 clutter-1.0 >= 1.26.0
Libs: -L${libdir} -lgtkcanvas-@API_VERSION@
Cflags: -I${includedir}/gtkcanvas-@API_VERSION@
